@startuml 13-mapa-eventos

title Diagrama de Componentes — Catálogo de Eventos y Flujo entre Servicios
header Message Broker = Redis Pub/Sub (no RabbitMQ todavía) — Proyecto.md §7.3

!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas
skinparam wrapWidth 220
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor Black
  BackgroundColor White
}
skinparam package {
  BorderColor Gray
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor LightYellow
  BorderColor Orange
}

package "Gateway" {
  rectangle "PlayerDisconnected\n(evento crudo)" as GW1
}

package "Room Service" {
  rectangle "RoomReady" as R1
  rectangle "PlayerRoomJoined" as R2
  rectangle "PlayerDisconnectedFromRoom" as R3
  rectangle "PlayerReconnected" as R4
  rectangle "RoomDestroyed" as R5
}

package "Game Service" {
  rectangle "GameStarted" as G1
  rectangle "ShotFired" as G2
  rectangle "PhaseChanged" as G3
  rectangle "PowerUsed" as G4
  rectangle "PowerCompensated" as G5
  rectangle "ShipsPlaced" as G6
  rectangle "ShipSunk" as G7
  rectangle "GameEnded" as G8
}

package "Timer Service" {
  rectangle "TimerEnd" as T1
  rectangle "TimerTick" as T2
}

package "Bot Service" {
  rectangle "BotDecision" as B1
}

package "Chat Service" {
  rectangle "ChatMessage" as C1
}

rectangle "Message Broker\n(Redis Pub/Sub)" as Broker #LightBlue

GW1 -down-> Broker
R1 -down-> Broker
R2 -down-> Broker
R3 -down-> Broker
R4 -down-> Broker
R5 -down-> Broker
G1 -down-> Broker
G2 -down-> Broker
G3 -down-> Broker
G4 -down-> Broker
G5 -down-> Broker
G6 -down-> Broker
G7 -down-> Broker
G8 -down-> Broker
T1 -down-> Broker
T2 -down-> Broker
B1 -down-> Broker
C1 -down-> Broker

Broker -up-> "Room Service" : consume(GameEnded,\nPlayerDisconnected)
Broker -up-> "Game Service" : consume(RoomReady, TimerEnd,\nPlayerDisconnectedFromRoom,\nPlayerReconnected, BotDecision)
Broker -up-> "Timer Service" : consume(PhaseChanged,\nRoomReady, PlayerDisconnectedFromRoom,\nPlayerReconnected)
Broker -up-> "Chat Service" : consume(PlayerRoomJoined)
Broker -up-> "Bot Service" : consume(ShotFired, PhaseChanged)
Broker -up-> "Gateway" : consume(PhaseChanged, TimerTick)\n"para reenviar al cliente"
Broker -up-> "Observability" : consume(*)\n"absolutamente todos"

note as N1
  **Garantías de entrega (Proyecto.md §6.4):**
  Redis Pub/Sub hoy = best-effort (si el
  consumidor no está conectado, el evento
  se pierde). RabbitMQ (at-least-once) queda
  documentado como evolución futura, NO como
  el broker actual.

  **Regla de independencia (§6.5):** ningún
  servicio crítico (Game, Timer) depende de
  uno no crítico (Chat, Observability, Bot)
  para funcionar.
end note

note as N2
  **Corrección de esta sesión:** el evento
  `PlayerDisconnected` del Gateway es "crudo"
  y solo lo consume Room Service. Room Service
  es quien decide y publica los eventos
  derivados `PlayerDisconnectedFromRoom` /
  `PlayerReconnected`, que sí consumen Game,
  Timer, Chat y Observability.
end note

@enduml
